        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure L 11. Labels. i Bulimus canaliculatus Pfeiffer, 1845 ii Drymaeus prestoni cancellata da Costa, 1906 iii Drymaeus castaneostrigatus da Costa, 1906 iv Bulimus castus Pfeiffer, 1847 v Bulimus catlowiae Pfeiffer, 1853 vi Bulimulus (Drymaeus) caucaensis da Costa, 1898 vii Bulimus ceratacme Pfeiffer, 1855." , "Figure 36. Drymaeus species. A-C Drymaeus (Drymaeus) boucardi da Costa, 1907, holotype NHMUK 1907.11.21.26 (H = 26.9) D-F Drymaeus (Drymaeus) buckleyi (Sowerby III, 1895), lectotype NHMUK 1907.11.21.48 (H = 27.3) G-I Drymaeus (Drymaeus) castaneostrigatus da Costa, 1906, holotype NHMUK 1907.11.21.13 (H = 20.4) J-L Drymaeus (Drymaeus) tigrinus (da Costa, 1898), lectotype NHMUK 1907.11.21.55 (H = 20.8). All enlarged." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/26762" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/26698" .

